## F. Structured AI Prompt  

### GOAL  
Build an Excel FX hedging model.

---

### INPUTS  

- FC_AMT = 20000000  
- S0_in = [spot rate]  
- F0_in = 1.0935  
- R_USD = [USD rate]  
- R_FC = [EUR rate]  
- K_PUT = S0_in  
- K_CALL = S0_in  
- PREM_PUT = 0.019  
- PREM_CALL = 0.024  
- T_DAYS = 365  

---

### MODEL  

**Forward:**  
USD_forward = FC_AMT × F0_in  

**Money Market:**  
EUR_borrowed = FC_AMT / (1 + R_FC)  
USD_today = EUR_borrowed × S0_in  
USD_mm = USD_today × (1 + R_USD)  

**Options:**  
USD_unhedged = FC_AMT × S_T  
USD_put = FC_AMT × MAX(S_T, K_PUT) − FC_AMT × PREM_PUT  
USD_call = FC_AMT × S_T − FC_AMT × PREM_CALL  

